kind: Tcaplus
metadata:
  name: tcaplus-sample
spec:
  checksum: "123"
  configMapTemplate:
    name: "tcaplus-configmap-example"
    data:
      demo.proto: |
        syntax = "proto3";
        package example;
        message Example {
          uint32 a = 1;
          uint32 b = 2;
          uint32 c = 3;
        }
```
使用上述配置文件创建 tcaplus 资源。创建结果：
```
marklu-MB2:samples $ k get tcaplus
NAME AGE
tcaplus-sample 19m
marklu-MB2:samples $ k get configmap
NAME DATA AGE
tcaplus-configmap-example 1 19m
```
可以查看 tcaplus-configmap-example 的属主关系：
```
